Added two options:
linkContainer - Allows you to wrap each link with a html tag, useful for the li tag for pagination in a list.
curTag - Instead of the previously hardcoded use of a "span" tag for current links, this allows you to set a html tag. Best when using lists to keep it 'a' and set a 'active' class using curPageLinkClassName.
